FBIS3-32144 "drlat023_a_94006" FBIS-LAT-94-023 Document Type:Daily Report 3 February 1994 CARIBBEAN Cuba German Airline Announces Possible Joint Venture FL0202161994 Havana Radio Progreso Network in Spanish 1200 GMT 2 Feb 94 FL0202161994 Havana Radio Progreso Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Text] LTU President Hans Joachim Driessen has announced that the German charter airline is going to study the possibility, with Cubanacan S.A., of forming a mixed civil aviation enterprise by 1995-96. The German businessman also offered to collaborate in promotions and advertising encouraging German tourist travel to Cuba. Another aspect is the possibility of increasing the German airline's flights from Dusseldorf to Cuba; nor did Driessen discard the idea of cruise ships.
